Spend less time preparing dinner and more time on the things you love doing  by preparing this flavourful slow cooker pulled chicken recipe.  Serve this juicy and delicious slow cooker pulled chicken dish with your favourite buns to create juicy burgers, or in tortillas with your favourite toppings to create delicious Mexican quesadillas. It can also be served with rice or pasta. ALSO TRY: Recipe of the day: Scrumptious spinach and feta scones This recipe was found on bbcgoodfood.com